txt.en: The death of Kranklob forces the Enemy to seek a new matron to foster their Warg-packs.
The Warg-pits of Dol Guldur are overseen by the goblin Athgrat and the Warg Kranklob, vile servants of the Enemy.
The ability of the Enemy to train their Wargs and Warg-riders has been hampered by the death of Athgrat.
